original_title: Eorzean Symphony: FINAL FANTASY XIV Orchestral Album Vol.3
overview: We are pleased to present the third FINAL FANTASY XIV orchestral arrangement album! Enjoy another exciting journey into the world of FFXIV through the intertwining of music and video.  Featuring songs from A Realm Reborn, Heavensward, Stormblood, Shadowbringers, and Endwalker, this Blu-ray disc allows you to enjoy full orchestra arrangement pieces performed at the FINAL FANTASY XIV ORCHESTRA CONCERT 2022 -Eorzean Symphony- in Japan!
title: Eorzean Symphony: FINAL FANTASY XIV Orchestral Album Vol.3
